	(text_box "These component values follow the typical application (Figure 8-1, page 14).\nAlternative values are listed in Table 8-2 (page 18) for 3.3 V output.\nThe typical voltage refence (Fb) is 0.596V.\n\nSpecs:\n	Use X7R ceramic capacitors\n	Use resistors with 1% maximum tolerance\n	Use ferrite-core inductors\n	Input Voltage range 8V to 28V (Page 14)\n\n "
